                      <SHORT-NAME>CddIpcDevErrorDetect</SHORT-NAME>
                      <DESC>
                        <L-2 L="EN">Switches the development error detection and notification on or off.</L-2>
                      </DESC>
                      <SCOPE>LOCAL</SCOPE>
